overview.en: ONOT is a kind of cryptocurrency which can freely circulate inside the ONO Value Network; It is the value certification of 'Attention Value' inside ONO SNS; ONOT holder can also obtain a large amount of dividends from the DApps within the ONO Value Network.
overview.zh: ONOT是ONO价值网络内自由流通的代币；是ONO SNS内兑现注意力价值的价值凭证；持有ONOT还可以获得ONO价值网络内DApps的大额分红。
